{"tid":1376531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要全城罷工，首先要港鐵同巴士公司帶頭","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T12:00:18.000Z","uid":84104,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a171566fd64e4c518ed7783903178dd6bbf1b957","tid":1376531,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"冇車搭，全世界唔洗開工<br />\n好多商户係因為擔心如果自己公司帶頭罷工<br />\n等於政治表態，<br />\n驚自己下場好似保礦力同吉野家咁<br />\n-支持示威者，比大陸玻璃心清算<br />\n-支持政府/黑警，比香港人杯葛<br />\n而打工仔亦會一樣驚罷工會冇咗份工<br />\n<br />\n而兩全其美嘅方法，就係斷交通！<br />\n冇咗港鐵同巴士，<br />\n班深藍dc9紅van9一定會好似打風咁坐地起價<br />\n打工仔大條道理返唔到工<br />\n咁唔夠人開工就自然開唔到舖<br />\n就算開到都冇人嚟行<br />\n咁商户自然就會齊齊被罷工一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家只需要安坐家中等記者會就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00d1989b2def639fb09b5502c9767eec408a698","tid":1376531,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b1d983b9b78b03a29c5ddce9dbcaf494c960177","tid":1376531,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5436ed8e8b1bdd892167aafbec285f76038ed716","tid":1376531,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:38:44.000Z","msg":"今次無大台，組織要下而上，<br />\n先加入公海，尋求共識！<br />\n<br />\n公墓員工業行動-公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LVypN0xVqlmnXAzSEP7oCg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLVypN0xVqlmnXAzSEP7oCg&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=02285565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LVypN0xVqlmnXAzSEP7oCg</a><br />\n<br />\n香港金融同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkfinancefellow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkfinancefellow&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=fa850863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkfinancefellow</a> <br />\n<br />\